 for 20p a piece. So yeah, I should get a shot at an item that I will &quot;just&quot; sell, becasue I'll turn around and use that &quot;filthy lucre&quot; and buy the spells that I need to be a viable soloer and grouper through the next couple levels. </p>&nbsp;<br>illovich<br>aka Viergang, 7th Hammer Wanderer-at-large, notary public of Surefall Glades<br>and if you don't like my ideas, you'll love my dog:&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://illovich.com/yoshi" target=_new>http://illovich.com/yoshi</a></td></td></tr>
